title: NFC South Breakdown + Baker Traded! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 7/7
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, we react to Baker Mayfield being traded to the Panthers! Will D.J. Moore be a top 12 fantasy WR? Get the fantasy football outlook for the Buccaneers, Saints, Falcons, and Panthers! Plus a new edition of Best Ball Breakdown taking a look at TE draft strategy. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for July 7th, 2022.

The 2022 Ultimate Draft Kit and Draft Analyzer are available NOW
